text: == Births == * April 14 – Emperor Go-Kogon of Japan (died 1374) * July 25 – Albert, Count of Holland (d. 1404) * King Albert of Sweden (died 1412) * Cyprian, Metropolitan of Moscow (died 1406) * Pope Gregory XI (died 1378) * Pope Innocent VII (died 1406) * Gao Qi, Chinese poet (died 1374) * Tamerlane, founder of the Timurid Empire (died 1405)
